column2: # = High output engine that provides more power than the standard engine of the same size
Fuel consumption ratings are shown in litres per 100 kilometres (L/100 km) and in miles per imperial gallon (mi./gal.)
Estimated annual fuel use is based on 20 000 km driven and a combined rating of 55 percent city and 45 percent highway.
Annual carbon dioxide emissions are based on estimated annual fuel use and fuel type.
